				<td colspan="2"><span>More than likely they'll be a 3/6/9/12/15 AA to increase the FT cap by one point per level.
<br />

<br />
Oh yeah, and for songs on Lucy, 'Reagents: Wooden Flutex1' <b><i>does not</b></i> mean the song will actually consume a Wooden Flute each and every time you successfully cast it. It only means that you need a wind instrument <b><i>equipped</i></b>. You can see the same for <a target="_new" href="http://lucy.allakhazam.com/spell.html?id=3375&amp;source=Live">Harmony of Sound</a> or <a target="_new" href="http://lucy.allakhazam.com/spell.html?id=1449&amp;source=Live">Melody of Ervaj</a> or <a target="_new" href="http://lucy.allakhazam.com/spell.html?id=719&amp;source=Live">Shauri's Sonorous Clouding</a>. All these songs merely require an instrument of the type to be equipped, not that they consume them on a successful cast. Can you imagine if you needed a flute in your inventory for every time you needed to restart Shauri's? </span></td>
