				<td colspan="2"><span>HUH!?!?  Do you ever charm now?  Do you have any FT now?  Do you have a clue?
<br />

<br />
Level 70 song.... 120m per cast.... 1 minute duration...
<br />

<br />
15FT = 16mana/tick (at least)... times 10 ticks per minute. ... = ... 160m regained during the duration of the charm
<br />

<br />
I currently have FT5 + MC3.  I swarm using the 90m/cast charm fairly often (I get small blocks of time to play sometimes)... I CANNOT RUN OUT OF MANA swarming.  And its mighty rare to have my charm go full duration.  In fact I can REGAIN mana swarming at my FT8 total now, albeit slowly.
<br />

<br />
FT15 has nothing to do with charming, even with a 120mana/cast charm.  FT15 is about fading... My FT8 is about fading, its overkill for the current charm.  
<br />

<br />
The way I figure it... with my current FT8 total... and the 120m charm... from full mana... killing 1 mob/minute... I could go nonstop for roughly 2 hours + before needed to regain mana...  If I slowed that pace a bit to say... 78 seconds per mob... I could go for more like 10 hours... I don't see anything to complain about.
<br />

<br />
Reys</span></td>
